README.md

Awesome

   [https://www.scirra.com/][68747470733a2f2f73312e636f6e7374727563742e6e6
   5742f696d616765732f763334372f75706c6f6164732f70726f647563742f322f646566
   61756c7469636f6e2f312f69636f6e2e706e67]

     You can create the game of your dreams. Build brain tickling
     puzzles, stunning platformers and immersive RPGs - or break the
     mould and make something new. Create what you want, how you want
     with [https://www.construct.net/]Construct.

     -- Ashley (Scirra Founder)

   This list includes all the best tools, tutorials and examples related
   to the awesome game development engines
   [https://www.scirra.com/construct2]Construct 2 and
   [https://www.construct.net/]Construct.

   [https://github.com/armaldio/awesome-construct/blob/master/contributing
   .md]How to contribute?

Contents

     * Community
     * Games Showcase
     * Hosting
     * Tools
     * Plugins/Behaviors/Effects
     * Tutorials
     * E-Books
     * Useful Links

Community

     * [https://discord.gg/8RJBHbX]Discord Server |
       [https://www.scirra.com/forum/there-is-a-construct-2-discord-server
       -chat-app-join-us_t181854]Scirra Forum Thread
     * [https://scirra.slack.com/]Slack Server |
       [https://www.scirra.com/forum/live-span-class-posthilit-chat-span-f
       or-scirra-com_p1003130?#p1003130]Scirra Forum Thread
     * [https://www.scirra.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=63692&start=0]FAQ
     * [https://www.scirra.com/forum]Forums
     * [http://stackoverflow.com/questions/tagged/construct-2]Stack
       Overflow
     * [https://www.reddit.com/r/construct/]Reddit
     * [https://twitter.com/constructteam]Twitter
     * [https://www.facebook.com/ConstructTeam/]Facebook

Games Showcase

     * [http://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=103535227]Ga
       mes on Steam - List of Steam games made with the engine.
     * [https://itch.io/games/tag-construct-2]Games on itch.io - List of
       itch.io games made with the engine.

Hosting

     * [http://www.itch.io/]itch.io - Platform where to host, showcase,
       promote or sell your games - Free.
     * [http://pages.github.com/]GitHub Pages - Platform where to host an
       exported game as a static website - Free.
     * [https://www.bitballoon.com/]BitBaloon - Platform where to host an
       exported game as a static website - Free/Paid.
     * [https://surge.sh/]Surge - Platform where to host an exported game
       as a static website - Free/Paid.
     * [https://zeit.co/now]Now - Platform where to host an exported game
       as a static website, a docker image or a nodejs server - Free/Paid.
     * [https://www.netlify.com/]Netlify - Platform where to host an
       exported game as a static website - Free/Paid.

Tools

     * [https://armaldio.itch.io/construct-2-plugin-manager]Plugin Manager
       - Addon-manager where you can download and host addons
       (Deprecated).
     * [https://rexrainbow.github.io/C2RexDoc/c2rexplugins.weebly.com/inde
       x.html]Rex's Plugins Tool - The personnal addon manager of
       Rex.Rainbow.
     * [https://github.com/armaldio/c2-addon-assistant]Addon Assistant -
       Construct addon development assistant

Plugins/Behaviors/Effects

     * [https://www.scirra.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=65170&start=0][Kyatri
       c] C2 Plugins and Behaviors List - Complete list of Plugins and
       Behaviours available on the forums.
     * [https://www.scirra.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=74374&start=0][Kyatri
       c] WebGL Effects List - Complete list of Effects available on the
       forums.

Tutorials

YouTube

     * [https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLmyh0_jcCzcoPTgHkm4CJSw_sdK
       5lPSb_][ArcadEdGames] Construct 2 Tutorials - YouTube channel about
       making all sort of stuff.
     * [https://www.youtube.com/user/ScirraVideos/playlists][ScirraVideos]
       Construct 2 Tutorials - Official Scirra's YouTube channel.
     * [https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLGdBDrsyOPm9XGiq1w_8DvbEQbH
       mkn7fx][C2Tuts 2D Game Development] Construct 2 Tutorials - General
       tutorials.
     * [https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLsJBMeqEdtggBJBiuX8bnF10ewH
       jdE20e][Nicholas Dingle] Construct 2 Tutorials - Number of
       tutorials covering different games you can create and different
       tricks.
     * [https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLq6aUvz66jtfnuyOKnPXO5dZly6
       CB8naA][John Maksym] Construct 2 Tutorial Series - General
       tutorials.
     * [https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLxwakQrJudt_NQlMp6oVuBdB-WI
       DKgoQ3][ConstructG] Create Simple Platformer Game With Construct 2
       - Tutorial about how to make a platformer game.
     * [https://www.youtube.com/user/kanedarkon/videos?view=0&flow=grid&so
       rt=da][Diego Lizarazo] Construct 2 Tutorials - Random stuff.
     * [https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLusL6SZZRaWr4zqm6GrQHmOuShw
       typRJ5][English Acorn] Construct 2 - Tutorials - General tutorials
       about the editor interface.
     * [https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLusL6SZZRaWqP6UmVPs9Ml8BRo2
       t-wvnT][English Acorn] Construct 2 - Plugins and Objects -
       Tutorials about plugins and how they work inside the Editor.
     * [https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCCR955dujboBxEN2VJlZwJw/playlists
       ][Game Development] Construct 2 - Tutorials - General tutorials.
     * [https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PL6gx4Cwl9DGAfHxsK6bji7trLS-
       N0nKF-][thenewboston] Game Development w/ Construct 2 Playlist -
       The official playlist for thenewboston Game Development.
     * [https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PL6gx4Cwl9DGAp287UuTE0-K7Ty-
       b8rGAX][thenewboston] Platform Game Development w/ Construct 2
       Playlist - Official playlist for thenewboston Platform Game
       Development.
     * [https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PL6gx4Cwl9DGDexNbWi0uPBP6bud
       uUZO3Q][thenewboston] Physics Puzzle Game Development w/ Construct
       2 Playlist - The official playlist for thenewboston Physics Puzzle
       Game Development Tutorials.
     * [https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLz66pfeeD4TcPN9kO7JlqiITpgi
       _WWgn7][LividProductions] Platformer Tutorials - This series will
       teach you how to make a platformer.
     * [https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCQkYeiHm9URZsa7nugUg1lw/playlists
       ][Jerementor] Construct 2 Tutorials - General tutorials.
     * [https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLdn9X5UVD8H1dEcWVjYU9E5fbpP
       GjZnQv][Kawaerri] Scirra Construct 2 Tutorial - General tutorials.
