     * [https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PL59F92017DA9887DB]Construct
       2 Tutorials - Breakout Clone - Learn how to create a Brakeout game.

Other Sources

     * [https://mva.microsoft.com/en-US/training-courses/game-development-
       with-construct-2-8355][MVA] Game Development with Construct 2
       (Basic) - Basic course about making games.
     * [https://mva.microsoft.com/en-US/training-courses/developing-window
       s-10-games-with-construct-2-16335][MVA] Developing Windows 10 Games
       with Construct 2 (Advanced) - Advanced course about making games.
     * [https://www.jerementor.com/programming-logic-made-easy-with-constr
       uct-2.html]Programming Logic MADE EASY with Construct 2! - General
       course about making games.
     * [https://www.udemy.com/learn-construct-2-creating-a-pixel-platforme
       r-in-html5/][Udemy FREE!] Learn Construct 2 - Creating a Pixel
       Platformer in HTML5.
     * [https://gamedevelopment.tutsplus.com/categories/construct-2][TutPl
       us] Construct 2 Tutorials - General tutorials.

E-Books

     * [https://www.scirra.com/blog/172/level-zero-free-construct-2-book]L
       evel Zero - Complete book on how to make games.

Useful Links

     * [https://game-assets.zeef.com/andre.antonio.schmitz]Game Assets by
       Andre Antonio Schmitzht - Resources and tools for creating assets
       used in games: graphics, modeling, animation, audio, music, video,
       maps and others.
     * [https://game-development.zeef.com/david.arcila]Game Development by
       David Arcila - "The biggest list of game development resources on
       the web".

